:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"弁護士による無料相談\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:13:\"lastBuildDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 06 Jun 2017 02:19:33 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"language\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"ja\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"generator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"https://wordpress.org/?v=4.7.5\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"item\";a:10:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"代表弁護士/山下江のラジオ出演のお知らせ\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/media/4807\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 05 Jun 2017 06:45:44 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"メディア\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/?p=4807\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:630:\"<p>代表弁護士/山下江がＲＣＣラジオ「京橋の杜情報局」に出演します。 交通事故の保険金の増額についてお話ししますので、お時間の許す方はぜひお聴きください。 放送日時：６月８日（木）１５：３５頃～ 番組名：ＲＣＣラジオ・京橋の [&#8230;]</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/media/4807\">代表弁護士/山下江のラジオ出演のお知らせ</a>は<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com\">【広島市-東広島市-呉市】山下江法律事務所</a>で公開された投稿です。</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"福田 一生\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1462:\"<p>代表弁護士/山下江がＲＣＣラジオ「京橋の杜情報局」に出演します。<br />\n 交通事故の保険金の増額についてお話ししますので、お時間の許す方はぜひお聴きください。</p>\n<p>放送日時：６月８日（木）１５：３５頃～<br />\n 番組名：ＲＣＣラジオ・京橋の杜情報局「ちょっと耳よりコーナー」<br />\n チャンネル：1350kHz<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/members/ko-yamashita\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3579\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/yamashita-ko.jpg?resize=210%2C210&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"山下江（やましたこう）-広島県出身の弁護士\" srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/yamashita-ko.jpg?w=210&amp;ssl=1 210w, https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/yamashita-ko.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 210px) 100vw, 210px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a><br />\n ↑写真をクリックすると山下江のプロフィールをご覧頂けます！</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/media/4807\">代表弁護士/山下江のラジオ出演のお知らせ</a>は<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com\">【広島市-東広島市-呉市】山下江法律事務所</a>で公開された投稿です。</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"第５回住宅博２０１７in広島\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/seminer/4797\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 02 Jun 2017 02:37:33 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"セミナー案内\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/?p=4797\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1410:\"<p><img width=\"1104\" height=\"1645\" src=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9c7edf03ce8cfee32f45dbb34facf766.jpg\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9c7edf03ce8cfee32f45dbb34facf766.jpg?w=1104&amp;ssl=1 1104w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9c7edf03ce8cfee32f45dbb34facf766.jpg?resize=201%2C300&amp;ssl=1 201w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9c7edf03ce8cfee32f45dbb34facf766.jpg?resize=768%2C1144&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9c7edf03ce8cfee32f45dbb34facf766.jpg?resize=687%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 687w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1104px) 100vw, 1104px\" /></p>\n<p>第５回住宅博２０１７in広島 マエダハウジング主催「第５回住宅博２０１７in広島」が開催されます。 最新のリフォームやリノベーション、水回り、不動産情報、新築情報などの他、DIYワークショップ、こども工務店など、ご家族で [&#8230;]</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/seminer/4797\">第５回住宅博２０１７in広島</a>は<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com\">【広島市-東広島市-呉市】山下江法律事務所</a>で公開された投稿です。</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"福田 一生\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7183:\"<p><img width=\"1104\" height=\"1645\" src=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9c7edf03ce8cfee32f45dbb34facf766.jpg\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9c7edf03ce8cfee32f45dbb34facf766.jpg?w=1104&amp;ssl=1 1104w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9c7edf03ce8cfee32f45dbb34facf766.jpg?resize=201%2C300&amp;ssl=1 201w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9c7edf03ce8cfee32f45dbb34facf766.jpg?resize=768%2C1144&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9c7edf03ce8cfee32f45dbb34facf766.jpg?resize=687%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 687w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1104px) 100vw, 1104px\" /></p><div class=\"content-post\">\n<h2>第５回住宅博２０１７in広島</h2>\n<div class=\"content-post\">\n<p><a href=\"https://www.maedahousing.co.jp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">マエダハウジング</a>主催「第５回住宅博２０１７in広島」が開催されます。<br />\n 最新のリフォームやリノベーション、水回り、不動産情報、新築情報などの他、DIYワークショップ、こども工務店など、ご家族でお楽しみ頂けるイベントです。<br />\n 特別セミナーでは、弊所の加藤泰弁護士と上級相続アドバイザー今井絵美が登壇します。<br />\n ぜひお立ち寄りください。</p>\n<p> 日　時： ２０１７年６月１７日（土）～１８日（日）１０：００～１７：００<br />\n 会　場： 広島県立広島産業会館・東展示館（<a href=\"https://www.google.co.jp/maps/place/%E5%BA%83%E5%B3%B6%E7%9C%8C%E7%AB%8B%E5%BA%83%E5%B3%B6%E7%94%A3%E6%A5%AD%E4%BC%9A%E9%A4%A8/@34.3805524,132.4674223,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x355aa21e8ee5ce4d:0x773d0b5257af60ff!8m2!3d34.380548!4d132.469611\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">広島市南区比治山本町12-18</a>）<br />\n 入　場： 無料<br />\n お問い合わせ：0120-164908（マエダハウジング）<br />\n <a href=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9c7edf03ce8cfee32f45dbb34facf766.jpg?ssl=1\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-4799\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9c7edf03ce8cfee32f45dbb34facf766.jpg?resize=201%2C300&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9c7edf03ce8cfee32f45dbb34facf766.jpg?resize=201%2C300&amp;ssl=1 201w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9c7edf03ce8cfee32f45dbb34facf766.jpg?resize=768%2C1144&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9c7edf03ce8cfee32f45dbb34facf766.jpg?resize=687%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 687w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/9c7edf03ce8cfee32f45dbb34facf766.jpg?w=1104&amp;ssl=1 1104w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 201px) 100vw, 201px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a>　<a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/02a0c42b375e61d08b1ab18d2b914e3e.jpg?ssl=1\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-4800\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/02a0c42b375e61d08b1ab18d2b914e3e.jpg?resize=210%2C300&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/02a0c42b375e61d08b1ab18d2b914e3e.jpg?resize=210%2C300&amp;ssl=1 210w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/02a0c42b375e61d08b1ab18d2b914e3e.jpg?resize=768%2C1096&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/02a0c42b375e61d08b1ab18d2b914e3e.jpg?resize=717%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 717w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/02a0c42b375e61d08b1ab18d2b914e3e.jpg?w=1104&amp;ssl=1 1104w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 210px) 100vw, 210px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a><br />\n ↑クリックすると拡大してご覧頂けます。</p>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"SH2\">6/17（土）13:00～　家族と資産を守る「家族信託」という新しい選択肢</h3>\n<p>平均寿命と健康寿命の差、約「１０年」。<br />\n この間に不動産・預貯金などの財産をどう管理するのか、という準備が相続の場面でも重要な鍵となります。新しい制度「家族信託」を中心に財産管理への備えについてわかりやすく説明します。<br />\n 受講特典：先着３０名様にエンディングノートプレゼント！<br />\n 講師：<a href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/members/%e4%bb%8a%e4%ba%95%e7%b5%b5%e7%be%8e\">山下江法律事務所　上級相続アドバイザー　今井 絵美</a><br />\n <a href=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/856be09576584fa345f076257161a4b7.jpg?ssl=1\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-4767\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/856be09576584fa345f076257161a4b7.jpg?resize=200%2C300&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/856be09576584fa345f076257161a4b7.jpg?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/856be09576584fa345f076257161a4b7.jpg?w=267&amp;ssl=1 267w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a></p>\n<h3 class=\"SH2\">6/18（日）13:00～　不動産にまつわる法律相談所</h3>\n<p>相続、賃貸、ご近所問題など、不動産にまつわるトラブルとその解決法を、今年３月、明石家さんまの「ホンマでっか!?TV」に「家族問題評論家」として出演した加藤弁護士が分かりやすく解説。<br />\n 受講特典：先着１０名様に「<a href=\"https://hiroshima-sozoku.com/890/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">相続・遺言のポイント５０</a>」！<br />\n 講師：<a href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/members/yasushi-kato\">山下江法律事務所　弁護士　加藤 泰</a><br />\n <a href=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/A02_7662.jpg?ssl=1\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-4798\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/A02_7662.jpg?resize=200%2C300&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/A02_7662.jpg?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/A02_7662.jpg?resize=768%2C1152&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/A02_7662.jpg?resize=683%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 683w, https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/A02_7662.jpg?w=1280&amp;ssl=1 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a>\n </p>\n</div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/seminer/4797\">第５回住宅博２０１７in広島</a>は<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com\">【広島市-東広島市-呉市】山下江法律事務所</a>で公開された投稿です。</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:126:\"代表/山下江が出演するラジオ番組「なやみよまるく~江さんの何でも法律相談~」６月放送内容\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/media/2423\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 29 May 2017 05:00:14 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"メディア\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/?p=2423\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:654:\"<p>■■ 2017年6月の番組内容 ■■ 6月5日 　ネット上に自分の顔を勝手にアップされた　 6月12日 　土地の共有持ち分を取得したい　 6月19日 　身近な人が突然逮捕されたら 6月22日 　クーリングオフについて教え [&#8230;]</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/media/2423\">代表/山下江が出演するラジオ番組「なやみよまるく~江さんの何でも法律相談~」６月放送内容</a>は<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com\">【広島市-東広島市-呉市】山下江法律事務所</a>で公開された投稿です。</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"福田 一生\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3784:\"<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #008080;\">■■ </span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2017年6月の番組内容 </span><strong><span style=\"color: #008080;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">■■ <br />\n </span></span></strong></span></p>\n<table border=\"1\" summary=\"\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 24px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\" align=\"center\">6月5日</td>\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">　ネット上に自分の顔を勝手にアップされた　</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 24px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\" align=\"center\">6月12日</td>\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">　土地の共有持ち分を取得したい　</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 24px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\" align=\"center\">6月19日</td>\n<td style=\"height: 24px;\">　身近な人が突然逮捕されたら</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 24.2px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 24.2px;\" align=\"center\">6月22日</td>\n<td style=\"height: 24.2px;\">　クーリングオフについて教えて</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff00ff;\">2016年4月より、放送時間が変更しました！</span></strong><br />\n </span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">＜新時間＞<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><strong>毎週月曜日 午後1時30分～</strong></span></span>（再放送時間：毎週木曜日 午前10時～）<br />\n <a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/（新）FMちゅーピーなやみよまるく画像.jpg?ssl=1\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3870\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/（新）FMちゅーピーなやみよまるく画像.jpg?resize=300%2C165&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"FMちゅーピーなやみよまるく江さんの何でも法律相談\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/（新）FMちゅーピーなやみよまるく画像.jpg?resize=300%2C165&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/（新）FMちゅーピーなやみよまるく画像.jpg?w=584&amp;ssl=1 584w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a><br />\n 2011年1月3日より<a href=\"http://chupea.fm/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u>FMちゅーピー</u></span></a>（76.6MHz）で、当事務所代表山下江が身近に起こったトラブルのご相談にお答えするラジオ番組<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">「なやみよまるく～江さんの何でも法律相談～」</span>が始まりました。<br />\n 放送は、<strong><span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">毎週月曜日午後1時30分～</span></strong>、<a href=\"http://chupea.fm/index.php?c=4-9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><u><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">聴取エリア</span></u></a>は、広島市域とその隣接エリアです。それ以外の地域の皆様には、インターネット経由でお聴き頂けます。<br />\n →<a href=\"http://www.simulradio.jp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><u>FMちゅーピーサイマルラジオ</u></span></a>　「ＦＭちゅーピー」の横の「放送を聴く」ボタンをクリックしてください。</span></p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/media/2423\">代表/山下江が出演するラジオ番組「なやみよまるく~江さんの何でも法律相談~」６月放送内容</a>は<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com\">【広島市-東広島市-呉市】山下江法律事務所</a>で公開された投稿です。</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"とうかさん大祭とゆかたできん祭に協賛\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/csr/4770\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 19 May 2017 01:11:45 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"社会貢献活動\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/?p=4770\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:608:\"<p>当事務所は、広島の人々に「浴衣の着始めの祭り」と親しまれている広島の伝統的なお祭りを応援するため、2017年6月2日(金)～4日(日)に開催される「とうかさん大祭」と「ゆかたできん祭」に協賛しています。 ↑とうかさん公式 [&#8230;]</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/csr/4770\">とうかさん大祭とゆかたできん祭に協賛</a>は<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com\">【広島市-東広島市-呉市】山下江法律事務所</a>で公開された投稿です。</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"福田 一生\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3552:\"<p>当事務所は、広島の人々に「浴衣の着始めの祭り」と親しまれている広島の伝統的なお祭りを応援するため、2017年6月2日(金)～4日(日)に開催される「<strong>とうかさん大祭</strong>」と「<strong>ゆかたできん祭</strong>」に協賛しています。<br />\n <a href=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/bf7d608793db306670d4144639c56e74.jpg?ssl=1\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-4771\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/bf7d608793db306670d4144639c56e74.jpg?resize=300%2C208&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/bf7d608793db306670d4144639c56e74.jpg?resize=300%2C208&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/bf7d608793db306670d4144639c56e74.jpg?resize=768%2C533&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/bf7d608793db306670d4144639c56e74.jpg?w=772&amp;ssl=1 772w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /><br />\n </a><strong>↑</strong><a href=\"http://www.toukasan.jp/kyousan.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">とうかさん公式ホームページ</a>に事務所名が記載されています。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/80e8594538897b82075aa2f017f70f6d.jpg?ssl=1\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-4785\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/80e8594538897b82075aa2f017f70f6d.jpg?resize=300%2C212&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/80e8594538897b82075aa2f017f70f6d.jpg?resize=300%2C212&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/80e8594538897b82075aa2f017f70f6d.jpg?resize=768%2C543&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/80e8594538897b82075aa2f017f70f6d.jpg?resize=1024%2C725&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/80e8594538897b82075aa2f017f70f6d.jpg?w=1122&amp;ssl=1 1122w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a>　<a href=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/afcdefd084be0c7b20653a65121b86f5.jpg?ssl=1\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-4786\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/afcdefd084be0c7b20653a65121b86f5.jpg?resize=300%2C212&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/afcdefd084be0c7b20653a65121b86f5.jpg?resize=300%2C212&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/afcdefd084be0c7b20653a65121b86f5.jpg?resize=768%2C543&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/afcdefd084be0c7b20653a65121b86f5.jpg?resize=1024%2C725&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/afcdefd084be0c7b20653a65121b86f5.jpg?w=1122&amp;ssl=1 1122w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a><br />\n↑パンフレットに事務所名が記載されています。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/csr/4770\">とうかさん大祭とゆかたできん祭に協賛</a>は<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com\">【広島市-東広島市-呉市】山下江法律事務所</a>で公開された投稿です。</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"【終了】「空き家、相続・贈与対策 無料セミナー」第二弾\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/seminer/4765\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 18 May 2017 07:52:52 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"セミナー案内\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/?p=4765\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1455:\"<p><img width=\"1240\" height=\"1754\" src=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/7d34e448bcdf7f9f5c4202627e848fc4.jpg\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/7d34e448bcdf7f9f5c4202627e848fc4.jpg?w=1240&amp;ssl=1 1240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/7d34e448bcdf7f9f5c4202627e848fc4.jpg?resize=212%2C300&amp;ssl=1 212w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/7d34e448bcdf7f9f5c4202627e848fc4.jpg?resize=768%2C1086&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/7d34e448bcdf7f9f5c4202627e848fc4.jpg?resize=724%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 724w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\" /></p>\n<p>マエダハウジング不動産・山下江法律事務所 共同開催 【空き家、相続・贈与対策 無料セミナー】第二弾 専門家が教える＜相続・贈与＞＜空き家活用＞のアレコレが満載！ ぜひご参加ください！ 日　時： ２０１７年５月２８日（日） [&#8230;]</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/seminer/4765\">【終了】「空き家、相続・贈与対策 無料セミナー」第二弾</a>は<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com\">【広島市-東広島市-呉市】山下江法律事務所</a>で公開された投稿です。</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"福田 一生\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5097:\"<p><img width=\"1240\" height=\"1754\" src=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/7d34e448bcdf7f9f5c4202627e848fc4.jpg\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/7d34e448bcdf7f9f5c4202627e848fc4.jpg?w=1240&amp;ssl=1 1240w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/7d34e448bcdf7f9f5c4202627e848fc4.jpg?resize=212%2C300&amp;ssl=1 212w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/7d34e448bcdf7f9f5c4202627e848fc4.jpg?resize=768%2C1086&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/7d34e448bcdf7f9f5c4202627e848fc4.jpg?resize=724%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 724w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1240px) 100vw, 1240px\" /></p><div class=\"content-post\">\n<h2>マエダハウジング不動産・山下江法律事務所 共同開催 【空き家、相続・贈与対策 無料セミナー】第二弾</h2>\n<div class=\"content-post\">\n<p>専門家が教える＜相続・贈与＞＜空き家活用＞のアレコレが満載！<br />\n ぜひご参加ください！</p>\n</div>\n<p>日　時： ２０１７年５月２８日（日）１４：００～１６：００<br />\n 会　場： 八丁堀マエダビル４Ｆ（<a href=\"https://www.google.co.jp/maps/place/%EF%BC%88%E6%A0%AA%EF%BC%89%E3%83%9E%E3%82%A8%E3%83%80%E3%83%8F%E3%82%A6%E3%82%B8%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B0+%E5%85%AB%E4%B8%81%E5%A0%80%E5%BA%97+%EF%BC%88%E3%83%9E%E3%82%A8%E3%83%80%E3%83%8F%E3%82%A6%E3%82%B8%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B0%E4%B8%8D%E5%8B%95%E7%94%A3+%E4%B8%8D%E5%8B%95%E7%94%A3%E3%81%84%E3%81%A1%E3%81%B0%EF%BC%89/@34.3954372,132.4597931,17z/data=%213m1%214b1%214m5%213m4%211s0x355aa2088e26d7e1:0x30957e13809d9271%218m2%213d34.3954328%214d132.4619818\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">広島市中区八丁堀１０－１４</a>）<br />\n 参加費： 無料<br />\n 要予約：０１２０－６３５５４６（不動産いちば）</p>\n<h3 class=\"SH2\">＜第一部＞家族と資産を守る「家族信託」という新しい選択肢</h3>\n<p>平均寿命と健康寿命の差、約「１０年」。<br />\n この間に不動産・預貯金などの財産をどう管理するのか、という準備が相続の場面でも重要な鍵となります。新しい制度「家族信託」を中心に財産管理への備えについてわかりやすく説明します。<br />\n 講師：<a href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/members/%e4%bb%8a%e4%ba%95%e7%b5%b5%e7%be%8e\">山下江法律事務所　上級相続アドバイザー　今井 絵美</a><br />\n <a href=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/856be09576584fa345f076257161a4b7.jpg?ssl=1\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-4767\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/856be09576584fa345f076257161a4b7.jpg?resize=200%2C300&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/856be09576584fa345f076257161a4b7.jpg?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i1.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/856be09576584fa345f076257161a4b7.jpg?w=267&amp;ssl=1 267w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a></p>\n<h3 class=\"SH2\">＜第二部＞早く、高く売却できる「ホームステージング」</h3>\n<p>「ホームステージング」とはナニ？から始まり<br />\n ●「１８ヶ月売れなかった空き家が５日で売れた！」<br />\n ●「空家をホームステージングで解決できた」<br />\n など、空家を出来るだけ早く、高く売る方法をお伝えします。<br />\n 講師：マエダハウジング不動産　宅地建物取引士　吉田 和美</p>\n<p> <a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/7d34e448bcdf7f9f5c4202627e848fc4.jpg?ssl=1\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-4766\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/7d34e448bcdf7f9f5c4202627e848fc4.jpg?resize=212%2C300&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/7d34e448bcdf7f9f5c4202627e848fc4.jpg?resize=212%2C300&amp;ssl=1 212w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/7d34e448bcdf7f9f5c4202627e848fc4.jpg?resize=768%2C1086&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/7d34e448bcdf7f9f5c4202627e848fc4.jpg?resize=724%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 724w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/7d34e448bcdf7f9f5c4202627e848fc4.jpg?w=1240&amp;ssl=1 1240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 212px) 100vw, 212px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a><br />\n ↑クリックすると拡大してご覧頂けます。</p>\n</div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/seminer/4765\">【終了】「空き家、相続・贈与対策 無料セミナー」第二弾</a>は<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com\">【広島市-東広島市-呉市】山下江法律事務所</a>で公開された投稿です。</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:123:\"＜YouTube更新！＞介護セミナー「介護事故裁判例から見える介護事故の予防策・対応策」Vol.3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/youtube/4762\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 18 May 2017 04:50:58 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"YouTube\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/?p=4762\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:661:\"<p>山下江法律事務所YouTubeチャンネルに動画を追加しました！ ぜひご覧ください↓ 【介護セミナー】 ＜介護事故裁判例から見える介護事故の予防策・対応策＞ Vol.3｢京都地裁の判決」 ↑クリックすると動画が再生します。</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/youtube/4762\">＜YouTube更新！＞介護セミナー「介護事故裁判例から見える介護事故の予防策・対応策」Vol.3</a>は<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com\">【広島市-東広島市-呉市】山下江法律事務所</a>で公開された投稿です。</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"