ro-for-business/4754\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 16 May 2017 02:45:02 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"KAIRO for BUSINESS\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/?p=4754\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1302:\"<p><img width=\"794\" height=\"1123\" src=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/KAIRO-for-BUSINESS.jpg\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/KAIRO-for-BUSINESS.jpg?w=794&amp;ssl=1 794w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/KAIRO-for-BUSINESS.jpg?resize=212%2C300&amp;ssl=1 212w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/KAIRO-for-BUSINESS.jpg?resize=768%2C1086&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/KAIRO-for-BUSINESS.jpg?resize=724%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 724w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 794px) 100vw, 794px\" /></p>\n<p>2015年度より、ニュースレター「KAIRO BIMONTHLY」（海路隔月版）を「KAIRO for BUSINESS」と改め、ますます内容を充実してみなさまにお届けします。発行月は、１月、５月、９月の年３回です。送付 [&#8230;]</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/kairo-for-business/4754\">KAIRO for BUSINESS　2017年5月号　VOL.34発刊</a>は<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com\">【広島市-東広島市-呉市】山下江法律事務所</a>で公開された投稿です。</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"福田 一生\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2918:\"<p><img width=\"794\" height=\"1123\" src=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/KAIRO-for-BUSINESS.jpg\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/KAIRO-for-BUSINESS.jpg?w=794&amp;ssl=1 794w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/KAIRO-for-BUSINESS.jpg?resize=212%2C300&amp;ssl=1 212w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/KAIRO-for-BUSINESS.jpg?resize=768%2C1086&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/KAIRO-for-BUSINESS.jpg?resize=724%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 724w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 794px) 100vw, 794px\" /></p><p>2015年度より、ニュースレター「KAIRO BIMONTHLY」（海路隔月版）を「KAIRO for BUSINESS」と改め、ますます内容を充実してみなさまにお届けします。発行月は、１月、５月、９月の年３回です。送付希望の方は、お気軽に当事務所までご連絡ください。<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/KAIRO_34_1705.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-4756\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/KAIRO-for-BUSINESS.jpg?resize=212%2C300&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/KAIRO-for-BUSINESS.jpg?resize=212%2C300&amp;ssl=1 212w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/KAIRO-for-BUSINESS.jpg?resize=768%2C1086&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/KAIRO-for-BUSINESS.jpg?resize=724%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 724w, https://i0.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/KAIRO-for-BUSINESS.jpg?w=794&amp;ssl=1 794w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 212px) 100vw, 212px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a><br />\n ↑クリックすると拡大してご覧頂けます。（全４頁）</p>\n<p> ＜内容＞<br />\n ・【Q&amp;A】そうだ、弁護士にきいてみよう！「下請法ってなに？」<br />\n ・「外国人留学生の雇用の注意点」<br />\n ・第19回企業法務セミナー報告<br />\n ・弁護士ON・OFF　青山慶子<br />\n ・事務局コラム「癒やしの時間。」<br />\n ・第20回企業法務セミナー案内<br />\n ・交通事故治療研修会開催<br />\n ・介護セミナー開催<br />\n ・NHKカルチャー教室で相続講座を開講中<br />\n ・加藤泰弁護士がフジテレビ「ホンマでっか！？TV」に出演</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/kairo-for-business/4754\">KAIRO for BUSINESS　2017年5月号　VOL.34発刊</a>は<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com\">【広島市-東広島市-呉市】山下江法律事務所</a>で公開された投稿です。</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:100:\"【受付中】第２０回企業法務セミナー「弁護士が解説 下請法のポイント」\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/seminer/4750\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 15 May 2017 06:30:53 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"セミナー案内\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/?p=4750\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1485:\"<p><img width=\"794\" height=\"1123\" src=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/8c5ca90d33a7033b4f81533913141aac.jpg\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/8c5ca90d33a7033b4f81533913141aac.jpg?w=794&amp;ssl=1 794w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/8c5ca90d33a7033b4f81533913141aac.jpg?resize=212%2C300&amp;ssl=1 212w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/8c5ca90d33a7033b4f81533913141aac.jpg?resize=768%2C1086&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/8c5ca90d33a7033b4f81533913141aac.jpg?resize=724%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 724w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 794px) 100vw, 794px\" /></p>\n<p>　山下江法律事務所では、３、７、１１月に企業法務セミナーを開催しています。次回セミナーの詳細は以下のとおりです。セミナー後に弁護士との会食をご希望の方と、会場近隣の店舗にて､会食の場を設けさせていただきます。セミナーの内 [&#8230;]</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/seminer/4750\">【受付中】第２０回企業法務セミナー「弁護士が解説 下請法のポイント」</a>は<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com\">【広島市-東広島市-呉市】山下江法律事務所</a>で公開された投稿です。</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"福田 一生\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6947:\"<p><img width=\"794\" height=\"1123\" src=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/8c5ca90d33a7033b4f81533913141aac.jpg\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/8c5ca90d33a7033b4f81533913141aac.jpg?w=794&amp;ssl=1 794w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/8c5ca90d33a7033b4f81533913141aac.jpg?resize=212%2C300&amp;ssl=1 212w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/8c5ca90d33a7033b4f81533913141aac.jpg?resize=768%2C1086&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/8c5ca90d33a7033b4f81533913141aac.jpg?resize=724%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 724w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 794px) 100vw, 794px\" /></p><div class=\"content-post\">\n<p>　山下江法律事務所では、３、７、１１月に企業法務セミナーを開催しています。次回セミナーの詳細は以下のとおりです。セミナー後に弁護士との会食をご希望の方と、会場近隣の店舗にて､会食の場を設けさせていただきます。セミナーの内容に関する質問や、企業法務などの法律に関する話をすることができ、また、普段なかなか弁護士に聞けないことを気軽に聞いてみるチャンスです。この機会をぜひご活用ください。</p>\n<h3 class=\"SH2\">【第２０回企業法務セミナーご案内】　</h3>\n<p>テーマ：「弁護士が解説 下請法のポイント」～「下請いじめ」をしない，させないために～<br />\n 日　時： ２０１７年７月２７日（木）<br />\n 　　　 《セミナー》１８：３０～２０：００<br />\n 　　　 《弁護士との会食》 セミナー終了後　※希望者のみ<br />\n 会　場： Ｌｅ ＲＥＶＥ八丁堀（ルレーヴ）<br />\n 　　　　（<a href=\"https://www.google.co.jp/maps/place/%E3%80%92730-0013+%E5%BA%83%E5%B3%B6%E7%9C%8C%E5%BA%83%E5%B3%B6%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%8C%BA%E5%85%AB%E4%B8%81%E5%A0%80%EF%BC%91%E2%88%92%EF%BC%98+%E3%82%A8%E3%82%A4%E3%83%88%E3%83%93%E3%83%AB/@34.3974539,132.4620701,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m8!1m2!2m1!1z44Ko44Kk44OI44OT44Or!3m4!1s0x355a98a826eb214d:0xf0c65e34bcf71a37!8m2!3d34.3974478!4d132.464229\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">広島市中区八丁堀1-8 エイトビル2F</a>）<br />\n 講　師： <a href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/members/shin-tanaka\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">副代表・弁護士/田中 伸</a><br />\n 受講料： 顧問会社様　　 無料<br />\n 　 　　 一般参加者様 　１名様につき 4,０００円　<br />\n 会　食：各自負担（お一人様4,000円程度の予定）　 　　　　　<br />\n 特　典： ご参加頂きました方は、1ヶ月以内に1時間の無料相談（１万円相当）ができます。</p>\n<p> 【セミナー内容】<br />\n下請法（下請代金支払遅延等防止法）は、下請取引の公正化・下請業者の利益保護を目的として制定された「下請いじめ」を規制する法律です。公正取引委員会は、昨年１２月、中小事業者の取引条件の改善を図る観点から、「下請法に関する運用基準」を改正し、新事業者による違反行為事例を大幅に追加しました。<br />\n本セミナーでは、前記の改正を踏まえて、下請法の概要のほか、どのような行為が「下請いじめ」として規制対象となるのか、分かりやすく解説します。</p>\n<p>\n 【懇親会内容】<br />\n セミナー後に弁護士との会食をご希望の方と、会場近隣の店舗にて､会食の場を設けさせていただきます（会費は各自負担となります。お一人様４,０００円程度の予定です）。人数の事前確認のため、お手数ですが裏面申込書にある会食の出欠欄にもご記入くださいますようお願いいたします。</div>\n<div class=\"content-post\"> </div>\n<div class=\"content-post\">◆ＷＥＢでお申し込みはこちら⇒<a href=\"http://goo.gl/2DLlcv\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://goo.gl/2DLlcv</a></div>\n<div class=\"content-post\">◆ＦＡＸでお申し込みはこちら⇒<a href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/seminer_20.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">第20回企業法務セミナー申込書</a></div>\n<div class=\"content-post\">◆お電話でお申込みはこちら⇒<a href=\"tel:0822230695\">０８２－２２３－０６９５</a>（担当：企業法務チーム秘書）</div>\n<div class=\"content-post\"> <br />\n<a href=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/8c5ca90d33a7033b4f81533913141aac.jpg?ssl=1\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-4751\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/8c5ca90d33a7033b4f81533913141aac.jpg?resize=212%2C300&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/8c5ca90d33a7033b4f81533913141aac.jpg?resize=212%2C300&amp;ssl=1 212w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/8c5ca90d33a7033b4f81533913141aac.jpg?resize=768%2C1086&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/8c5ca90d33a7033b4f81533913141aac.jpg?resize=724%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 724w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/8c5ca90d33a7033b4f81533913141aac.jpg?w=794&amp;ssl=1 794w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 212px) 100vw, 212px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a> <a href=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/140f082c03b72621c0fa26de81987652.jpg?ssl=1\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-4752\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/140f082c03b72621c0fa26de81987652.jpg?resize=212%2C300&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/140f082c03b72621c0fa26de81987652.jpg?resize=212%2C300&amp;ssl=1 212w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/140f082c03b72621c0fa26de81987652.jpg?resize=768%2C1086&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/140f082c03b72621c0fa26de81987652.jpg?resize=724%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 724w, https://i2.wp.com/www.law-yamashita.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/140f082c03b72621c0fa26de81987652.jpg?w=794&amp;ssl=1 794w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 212px) 100vw, 212px\" data-recalc-dims=\"1\" /></a></div>\n<div class=\"content-post\"> </div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/seminer/4750\">【受付中】第２０回企業法務セミナー「弁護士が解説 下請法のポイント」</a>は<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.law-yamashita.com\">【広島市-東広島市-呉市】山下江法律事務所</a>で公開された投稿です。</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:123:\"＜YouTube更新！＞介護セミナー「介護事故裁判例から見える介護事故の予防策・対応策」Vol.2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/youtube/4714\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 01 May 2017 07:26:57 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"YouTube\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"https://www.law-yamashita.com/?p=4714\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\